        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The best three day excursion, as far as I can see, is the same as the first of the two day trips until you reach Lake Tenaya.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
