        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "Next morning climb Mount Hoffman; thence push on past Tenaya Lake into the Tuolumne Meadows and establish a central camp near the Soda Springs, from which glorious excursions can be made at your leisure.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "It is in the heart of the High Sierra east of Yosemite, eight thousand five hundred to nine thousand feet above the level of the sea.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000002_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000002_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The gray, picturesque Cathedral Range bounds it on the south; a similar range or spur, the highest peak of which is Mount Conness, on the north; the noble Mounts Dana, Gibbs, Mammoth, Lyell, McClure and others on the axis of the Range on the east; a heaving, billowing crowd of glacier polished rocks and Mount Hoffman on the west.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "Tracing the river, we find that it forks a mile above the Soda Springs, the main fork turning southward to Mount Lyell, the other eastward to Mount Dana and Mount Gibbs.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "Along both forks strips of meadow extend almost to their heads.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The most beautiful portions of the meadows are spread over lake basins, which have been filled up by deposits from the river.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000004_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000004_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The principal grass of these meadows is a delicate calamagrostis with very slender filiform leaves, and when it is in flower the ground seems to be covered with a faint purple mist, the stems of the panicles being so fine that they are almost invisible, and offer no appreciable resistance in walking through them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000004_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000004_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "Along the edges of the meadows beneath the pines and throughout the greater part of the Valley tall ribbon leaved grasses grow in abundance, chiefly bromus, triticum and agrostis.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "In October the nights are frosty, and then the meadows at sunrise, when every leaf is laden with crystals, are a fine sight.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The excursion to the top of Mount Dana is a very easy one; for though the mountain is thirteen thousand feet high, the ascent from the west side is so gentle and smooth that one may ride a mule to the very summit.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000008_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000008_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "To the eastward you gaze far out over the desert plains and mountains of the \"Great Basin,\" range beyond range extending with soft outlines, blue and purple in the distance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000008_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000008_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "To the southward there is a well defined range of pale gray extinct volcanoes, and though the highest of them rises nearly two thousand feet above the lake, you can look down from here into their circular, cup like craters, from which a comparatively short time ago ashes and cinders were showered over the surrounding sage plains and glacier laden mountains.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "To the westward the landscape is made up of exceedingly strong, gray, glaciated domes and ridge waves, most of them comparatively low, but the largest high enough to be called mountains; separated by canyons and darkened with lines and fields of forest, Cathedral Peak and Mount Hoffman in the distance; small lakes and innumerable meadows in the foreground.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "Northward and southward the great snowy mountains, marshaled along the axis of the Range, are seen in all their glory, crowded together in some places like trees in groves, making landscapes of wild, extravagant, bewildering magnificence, yet calm and silent as the sky.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "Some eight glaciers are in sight.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "It is about eight miles long and from two thousand to three thousand feet deep.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "At one place near the summit careful climbing is necessary, but it is not so dangerous or difficult as to deter any one of ordinary skill, while the views are glorious.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "These spurs like distinct ranges meet at your feet; therefore you look at them mostly in the direction of their extension, and their peaks seem to be massed and crowded against one another, while immense amphitheaters, canyons and subordinate ridges with their wealth of lakes, glaciers, and snow fields, maze and cluster between them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000012_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000012_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "A more interesting problem than a walk over a glacier thus sculptured and adorned is seldom presented to the mountaineer.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "And it is all the more interesting since it is the highest and most enduring remnant of the great Tuolumne Glacier, whose traces are still distinct fifty miles away, and whose influence on the landscape was so profound.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The McClure Glacier, once a tributary of the Lyell, is smaller.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The canyon begins near the lower end of the meadows and extends to the Hetch Hetchy Valley, a distance of about eighteen miles, though it will seem much longer to any one who scrambles through it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "It is from twelve hundred to about five thousand feet deep, and is comparatively narrow, but there are several roomy, park like openings in it, and throughout its whole extent Yosemite natures are displayed on a grand scale-domes, El Capitan rocks, gables, Sentinels, Royal Arches, Glacier Points, Cathedral Spires, etc",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "Its falls and cascades are innumerable.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000016_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000016_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The sheer falls, except when the snow is melting in early spring, are quite small in volume as compared with those of Yosemite and Hetch Hetchy; though in any other country many of them would be regarded as wonders.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000016_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000016_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The most showy and interesting of them are mostly in the upper part of the canyon, above the point of entrance of Cathedral Creek and Hoffman Creek.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000016_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000016_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "For miles the river is one wild, exulting, on rushing mass of snowy purple bloom, spreading over glacial waves of granite without any definite channel, gliding in magnificent silver plumes, dashing and foaming through huge boulder dams, leaping high into the air in wheel like whirls, displaying glorious enthusiasm, tossing from side to side, doubling, glinting, singing in exuberance of mountain energy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "There is not a dull step all the way.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "My own Sierra trip was ten years long.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "Other Trips From The Valley",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "Another fine trip was up, bright and early, by Avalanche Canyon to Glacier Point, along the rugged south wall, tracing all its far outs and ins to the head of the Bridal Veil Fall, thence back home, bright and late, by a brushy, bouldery slope between Cathedral rocks and Cathedral spires and along the level Valley floor.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "The Tuolumne grove was passed on the Big Oak Flat road, the Merced grove by the Coulterville road and the Mariposa grove by the Raymond and Wawona road.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000026_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000026_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "All the High Sierra excursions that I have sketched cost from a dollar a week to anything you like.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-598_127704_000026_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/598/127704/598_127704_000026_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-598",
        "content": "None of mine when I was exploring the Sierra cost over a dollar a week, most of them less.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]